data.description: Great home near Toledo Hospital , close to everthing and short drive to the rest of Toledo! Finished basement and 2 full baths! extra long garage (2 cars end to end is possible). see new photos after maid!  Very well priced vs the area! basement rec room was finished and has great possibilties!
